item.title: CVE-2023-39437|2024-10-11T22:21:09.655Z -- sap_se -- sap%20business%20one
item.description: SAP business One allows - version 10.0, allows an attacker to insert malicious code into the content of a web page or application and gets it delivered to the client, resulting to Cross-site scripting. This could lead to harmful action affecting the Confidentiality, Integrity and Availability of the application.
